column5: So it's no good after all.
column11: So it's no good after all.

column5: The Beast King won't wake up...
column11: The Beast King won't wake up...

column4:
完全なライオンハートが
なければ……。
column5: Not without a complete Lion Heart...
column11: Not without a complete Lion Heart...

column4: もう、すべてを出し尽くした。
column5: Ugh, but I've already tried everything I could think of.
column11: Ugh, but I've already tried everything I could think of.

column4:
これ以上どうすることも
できない。
column5: There's nothing more I can do.
column11: There's nothing more I can do.

column4:
私では
獣王を覚醒させられない。
column5: I can't awaken the Beast King.
column11: I can't awaken the Beast King.

column4:
天才だ神童だといわれて
いい気になって……。
column5: Even though people have always called me a naturally-gifted prodigy...
column11: Even though people have always called me a naturally gifted prodigy...

column4:
何が天才よ。
結局、私にはできなかった。
column5:
What gift?
In the end, I can't do anything.
column11:
What gift?
